data.description: Welcome to this charming single-family home, boasting three bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms; also, there is a bonus room on the bottom floor. Nestled in a desired neighborhood, this property is an ideal haven for a starter home.   As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere, highlighted by an open and airy floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The heart of the home is the spacious kitchen, featuring modern appliances and ample counter space, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guests.  Step outside to discover the large backyard, a versatile outdoor area where your imagination can run wild. Whether you're hosting summer barbecues, enjoying family gatherings, or simply soaking up the sun, this space is sure to impress. The covered patio adds to the allure, offering a shaded spot to relax and enjoy the outdoors, regardless of the weather.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. Schedule a visit today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience!  Conveniently located with easy commute to Joint Base Andrews, JBAB, Ft Belvoir, Ft Myers, Indian Head NAS, Beltway 495, Hwy 301, & Hwy 210.
